description.text:
To include a build plate selector in your Customizer script, use utils/build_plate.scad and include the following code:
//for display only, doesn't contribute to final object<br />
build_plate_selector = 0; //[0:Replicator 2,1: Replicator,2:Thingomatic,3:Manual]
//when Build Plate Selector is set to &quot;manual&quot; this controls the build plate x dimension<br />
build_plate_manual_x = 100; //[100:400]
//when Build Plate Selector is set to &quot;manual&quot; this controls the build plate y dimension<br />
build_plate_manual_y = 100; //[100:400]
build_plate(build_plate_selector,build_plate_manual_x,build_plate_manual_y);
